Clemente Sentino, Jennalyn's 45-year-old father, said he was grateful for government aid, but seemed confident he could support his child and his partner.

He and the child's mother, Dailin Cabigayan, 27, are not yet married. 'She just happened to get pregnant. But we do have plans to get married,' said Mr Sentino, a van driver.

